metadata.name: Moon Ape Malbox #1
metadata.description:
Collection of 750 mystery boxes which, when sold out, will reveal a prize from one of three categories. What could be in the box: 2 x 1/1 (Gold tickets) 60 x Genesis Moon Apes 688 x Whitelist Discount for our Season Two Collection
 All revealed prizes are equal to, or greater than, the original mint price
